Recommended tools and libraries:

autoconf 2.52g
automake 
gcc 3.0.3
gmp 4.0.1      (configure with -fexceptions *)
cln 1.1.4
ginac 1.0.4    (apply patches **)
fi_lib++ 2.0   (apply patches ***)


(*)
Your configure command should be something like

CPPFLAGS=-fexceptions my/path/to/gmp-4.0.1/configure --prefix=/usr/local


(**)
cd my/path/to/GiNaC-1.0.4/
patch -p1 <my/path/to/purrs/infrastructure/patch_ginac-1.0.4 

(***)
cd my/path/to/interval/
patch -p1 <my/path/to/purrs/infrastructure/patch_filib++-2.0
